Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//--------------------OPCN---------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.16,0:00:33.97,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「いま！」という　この瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:39.40,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}なんだって　音楽に　出来たらいいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.40,0:00:44.18,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}まだ　全力で　やり切ってない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.18,0:00:46.90,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}悔し涙　拭ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:50.43,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}青春のフレージング
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.43,0:00:55.46,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}奇跡が　努力の　先にあるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:01:01.15,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}限界は　あたしが決める
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.15,0:01:03.31,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}響け
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.31,0:01:10.17,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}もう一回　大げさな夢を　探しにいこう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.17,0:01:13.78,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}止めない　勇気こそ　強さ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.78,0:01:20.57,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}何百回　挑戦かさねて　ここまで来た
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.57,0:01:24.97,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}チャンスの神様　みててね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.97,0:01:27.55,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}忘れたくないメロディ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.55,0:01:30.22,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}離したくないメロディ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.22,0:01:33.25,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}輝きに変えて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.91,0:01:38.28,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想いよ　届け…！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.16,0:00:33.97,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「此时此刻」的这个瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:39.40,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}希望能以音乐将其铭刻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.40,0:00:44.18,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}还未拼尽全力到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.18,0:00:46.90,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不断拭去的悔恨泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:50.43,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}是青春的分句
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.43,0:00:55.46,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}若是努力之后便会有奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:01:01.15,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那极限由我来决定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.15,0:01:03.31,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}吹响吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.31,0:01:10.17,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}再一次去追寻那庞大的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.17,0:01:13.78,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}强大就是永不放弃的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.78,0:01:20.57,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}经历数百次的挑战　来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.57,0:01:24.97,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}请机会之神看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.97,0:01:27.55,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不想忘记的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.55,0:01:30.22,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不愿放开的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.22,0:01:33.25,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}变为耀眼的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.91,0:01:38.28,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}将这份心意　传递出去…！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//--------------------EDCN---------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.92,0:22:25.42,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}割り切れない想いを力に変えてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.42,0:22:29.80,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}無謀だと笑われた　何度も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.80,0:22:33.64,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}毎日が冒険で　青春で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.64,0:22:38.39,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}新しい音と出会っては磨いてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.39,0:22:42.44,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}本気でやったからこそ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.80,0:22:47.11,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}こわい瞬間もあるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.11,0:22:47.92,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}届けたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.00,0:22:48.82,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}伸ばしたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.82,0:22:49.62,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}奏でたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.64,0:22:50.40,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}叶えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.40,0:22:55.28,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}もう一度息を吹き込む　明日へと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.57,0:22:59.41,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}タクトに導かれてここまで来たよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.41,0:23:03.46,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたと来たんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.46,0:23:05.92,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}奏でているのは人生だ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.96,0:23:07.84,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}響くのは感情だ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.84,0:23:12.88,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ずっと忘れないからね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.88,0:23:16.68,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}光る音が涙を照らしてくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.68,0:23:21.14,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}辛いことばかりじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.14,0:23:26.66,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}だっていつも　いつも楽しかった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.68,0:23:28.57,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}そうでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.57,0:23:32.28,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ヴィヴァーチェ！歌え　五線の上で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.65,0:23:39.33,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ヴィヴァーチェ！響け　遠くの春に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.92,0:22:25.42,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}青春的苦涩变为了前进的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.42,0:22:29.80,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}年少冲动让我无数次被嘲笑声掩埋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.80,0:22:33.64,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}每天都在冒险　挥洒青春
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.64,0:22:38.39,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不断磨练期待与新的乐声邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.39,0:22:42.44,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}正因为全身心的付出
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.80,0:22:47.11,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}自然会有害怕的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.11,0:22:47.92,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想要传递
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.00,0:22:48.82,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想要触及
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.82,0:22:49.62,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想要演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.64,0:22:50.40,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想要实现
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.40,0:22:55.28,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}再一次向着奏响的明天迈进
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.57,0:22:59.41,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}遵循指挥棒的指引来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.41,0:23:03.46,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}与你携手一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.46,0:23:05.92,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}正在奏响的是人生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.96,0:23:07.84,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}余音缭绕的是情感
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.84,0:23:12.88,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}一直都无法忘怀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.88,0:23:16.68,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}耀眼的乐声将我们的泪水照亮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.68,0:23:21.14,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}并非全是辛酸经历
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.14,0:23:26.66,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}因为　一路走来有许多快乐伴随着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.68,0:23:28.57,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}没错吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.57,0:23:32.28,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}vivace！于五线谱之上唱响吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.65,0:23:39.33,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}vivace！向着远处胜利的春天吹响吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,--------------------PART--------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.50,0:00:04.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香  现在立刻说你要退部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.41,0:00:08.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈  我不想退部…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.74,0:00:14.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这次轮到我们去支持她了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.94,0:01:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.08,0:01:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:01:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是姐姐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.86,0:02:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈  我也想吹那个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.28,0:02:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你来说吹那个还有点早
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.72,0:02:23.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四年级开始才能加入
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.82,0:02:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我升到四年级就可以去吹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.88,0:02:30.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢  可以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.29,0:02:42.11,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1000,720)\bord1.5\blur2\fad(500,0)}感冒狂想曲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.22,0:02:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了我从一开始就是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.48,0:02:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可你还有一年就能毕业了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.35,0:02:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等到那时就晚了  必须现在就抓紧时间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.76,0:02:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  为什么突然要去学什么美容师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:56.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.12,0:02:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是从中学时就说想学了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.76,0:03:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时是妈妈你不同意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.64,0:03:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以来我都对妈妈说的话言听计从
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.46,0:03:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部忍耐下来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.32,0:03:10.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为我是姐姐  一直忍着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻美子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.28,0:03:18.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是转校还是报考大学  其实都不是我的意愿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.80,0:03:22.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当初也想像久美子那样继续社团活动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:24.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想放弃长号的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.58,0:03:30.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你那么有想法  那就应该在进大学前说不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不想想是谁让我难以开口的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实  我们可能给你的抉择带来了压力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:47.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  最终决定去考大学的人是你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:49.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:55.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你真的要退学  那就从这个家里出去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生活费和成为美容师的费用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.38,0:03:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都由你自己去解决
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.33,0:04:02.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  孩子他爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.12,0:04:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别以为追求理想不用付出任何代价
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.04,0:04:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的话太过以自我为中心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.08,0:04:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是认真的  就让我看看你的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻美子  妈妈不会说要你离开的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.42,0:04:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.40,0:04:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得姐姐是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.66,0:04:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.15,0:04:38.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:42.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「我当初不想放弃长号的」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.31,0:04:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这句话在我脑中挥之不去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.96,0:04:51.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从没想过姐姐原来有那种想法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.62,0:04:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐你为什么要放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.76,0:04:56.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.96,0:04:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和姐姐一起吹奏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.01,0:05:00.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.08,0:05:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:06.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说了你烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再说乱七八糟的话就把你的嘴缝上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:21.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻美子姐打算不念大学了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.45,0:05:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么会知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.37,0:05:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妈听人说的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.60,0:05:29.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明叫我不要去外面说  自己却…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.94,0:05:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在大学里发生了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.55,0:05:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哪知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从姐姐上大学之后我们就没怎么说过话了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.22,0:05:46.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  接下来是13号
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.27,0:05:49.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,田中明日香  现在归队
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有闲情雅致开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香学姐在车站大楼演奏会之后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.82,0:05:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord2.5\fsp3}至少和我们联络一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕竞赛会越来越迫在眉睫  她也几乎没有来练习
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:58.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord2.5\fsp3}有太多事要处理  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.70,0:06:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都很担心你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.70,0:06:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要看了消息却不回
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:05.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说了很多遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.02,0:06:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会给大家添麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:08.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话虽如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:10.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好  大家坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.57,0:06:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好  情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.96,0:06:14.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄前你还是老样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.63,0:06:19.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.82,0:06:22.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这可算是在夸你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.16,0:06:25.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那的是和往常一样的明日香学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.18,0:06:29.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  再次注视这张许久未见的侧脸时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.34,0:06:31.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一股无法抗拒的不安充斥了全身
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:35.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.01,0:06:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香学姐你不会退部的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.49,0:06:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会退部的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.94,0:06:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会退…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.86,0:06:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再那么烦人我就把你的嘴缝上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.31,0:06:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了黄前  期中考试你能应付吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:06:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有担心过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:07:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不觉得进入高中后课程变难了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.11,0:07:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…数学确实…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.83,0:07:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来教你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.89,0:07:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看  下周练习会早结束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来家里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家里？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.42,0:07:15.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香学姐的家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愿意？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.64,0:07:19.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是不愿意  只是觉得有点突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:24.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不必担心  那天到晚上为止只有我一个人在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.15,0:07:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.56,0:07:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说在前面  你要一个人来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.75,0:07:30.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.77,0:07:33.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样比较能集中精神不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.86,0:07:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那约好了哦  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:42.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.80,0:07:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.34,0:07:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被人邀请去家里了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:46.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.76,0:07:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.56,0:07:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她为什么这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.27,0:07:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非是你说了什么惹到她的话了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:01.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:06.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香学姐从第二天起又完全不来社团了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.26,0:08:08.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这演奏  我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.90,0:08:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我说出真实的感想  那就是感觉苦闷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.40,0:08:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然开始上课了  练习的时间少
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你们仍能维持暑假时的乐声  这点我觉得很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过比起那时  大家的演奏好呆板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.89,0:08:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,声音起伏不定  听着让人感觉难受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.64,0:08:30.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非是因为全国大赛所以很紧张？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.58,0:08:36.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家看上去完全没有享受其中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.42,0:08:38.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一副泷那样的可怕表情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.68,0:08:40.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的表情一点不可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.02,0:08:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说没有自知之明的人真让人头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.20,0:08:46.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和许多学校的人都说过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.43,0:08:49.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这人其实不太喜欢竞赛会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.90,0:08:53.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为只要努力去吹奏  是金是银无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能这话你们已经听烂了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.73,0:08:58.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓音乐就是要沉浸享受于乐声中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.28,0:09:00.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是在意金奖银奖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而让演奏变得紧张  呆板  苦闷那就没有意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.62,0:09:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要明快  开心  愉悦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来重复一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:10.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明快…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.95,0:09:12.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再明快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.68,0:09:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明快  开心  愉悦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.64,0:09:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  那么我顺次说一下改进的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:20.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是悠风
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.34,0:09:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没有听到声音  你刚才真有在吹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.35,0:09:27.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有在吹…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.18,0:09:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许是因为只有一个人  但声音太小了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.95,0:09:33.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平时那个很棒的学姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.91,0:09:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戴红色眼镜的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.15,0:09:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香学姐她…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.26,0:09:39.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天请假
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.23,0:09:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这么重要的时期？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.29,0:09:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  要吹得再响一点才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.32,0:09:49.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.55,0:09:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.28,0:09:58.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.44,0:09:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是有点流鼻涕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.92,0:10:02.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.03,0:10:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想替你量量体温
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.59,0:10:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是量体温的力道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.22,0:10:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点用力过度了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.99,0:10:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你发烧了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.52,0:10:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.31,0:10:19.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:21.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不行的  不如你今天先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.44,0:10:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是现在你倒下的话  竞赛会就没有人吹悠风了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.46,0:10:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  还有可能会传染给周围的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.18,0:10:31.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.11,0:10:34.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东西我来收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.12,0:10:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你准备回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.42,0:10:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.74,0:10:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久美子  你要回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.34,0:10:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  好像有点感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.62,0:10:46.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧  要我陪你一起回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.10,0:10:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  没事  而且也不能传染给你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.72,0:10:51.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.36,0:10:57.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次可能真挺严重的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.46,0:10:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.11,0:11:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.04,0:11:04.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感冒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.98,0:11:09.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  前辈让我早点回家休息不要让感冒加重
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.12,0:11:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟接下来就是全国大赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.14,0:11:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是休息下比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.60,0:11:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过话说回来  没想到能进全国大赛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.50,0:11:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个老师真的好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.50,0:11:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵你呢  学习怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.24,0:11:27.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  虽然之前的模拟考合格了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.46,0:11:30.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过重要的接下来的正式考试
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.72,0:11:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.18,0:11:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.27,0:11:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:35.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵你有去过明日香学姐的家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没  怎么这么问
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.38,0:11:46.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被她邀请了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.34,0:11:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.83,0:11:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看不出她是会说这种话的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.76,0:11:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.10,0:12:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来  我前些时候有看到她很早就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  她好像现在和父母有些争执
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.34,0:12:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连社团活动也请假了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.50,0:12:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.00,0:12:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.72,0:12:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为明日香什么事都能做好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.18,0:12:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我一直觉得她和这种事是沾不上边的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.46,0:12:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得也许在她看来据理力争是愚蠢的人才做的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定没有那回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.18,0:12:44.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.84,0:12:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过感觉自己松了一口气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她原来也是个普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.98,0:12:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.24,0:13:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的笑容仿佛裹在毛毯里的寒冰一般
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人感到很不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.04,0:13:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这段还有点快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.18,0:13:22.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:23.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久美子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她刚才联系说今天请假
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.50,0:13:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.40,0:13:30.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.26,0:13:33.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是感冒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.32,0:13:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.69,0:13:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊  黄前同学也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.36,0:13:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.76,0:13:40.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:43.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的合奏就让中川同学参加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.68,0:13:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心别让肩膀受凉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.04,0:13:47.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.65,0:13:50.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈要出去买东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.40,0:13:53.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么想要的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:55.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布丁  不要抹茶味的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.70,0:13:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:13:58.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.70,0:13:59.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该在房间里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.26,0:14:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久美子想演奏什么乐器呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.33,0:14:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为姐姐在吹长号  所以我也想吹长号
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.71,0:14:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长号吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.66,0:14:34.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠风怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:37.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠风？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个乐器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.62,0:14:42.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亮晶晶的  很帅气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.31,0:14:46.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠风…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.66,0:14:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给  这是初学者用的指南书
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.50,0:14:52.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  这是专业乐手演奏的悠风号的CD
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.04,0:14:54.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家之后听听看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:14:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.76,0:15:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们先从如何吹出声音开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.64,0:15:01.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:07.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒  真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.88,0:15:13.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是姐姐教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.62,0:15:15.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个不错的姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.30,0:15:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  姐姐很帅气的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.52,0:15:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.72,0:15:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.51,0:15:48.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多30分钟前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.72,0:15:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看你睡着了  叫醒你不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.36,0:15:53.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.38,0:15:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.35,0:15:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么来我家了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.17,0:15:56.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来探病
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.40,0:15:59.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.84,0:16:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能开灯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.88,0:16:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.32,0:16:06.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然川岛同学她们也很想来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.29,0:16:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过练习结束的比较晚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.64,0:16:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟小绿家是反方向的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.97,0:16:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是川岛同学给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.05,0:16:25.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布丁是加藤同学买的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.91,0:16:27.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.98,0:16:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:31.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是想吃这种普通的布丁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.60,0:16:32.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这张CD…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是悠风的所以就带来给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.32,0:16:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你已经有了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.92,0:16:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.56,0:16:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好想要听呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.53,0:16:48.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.68,0:16:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.33,0:17:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好听
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.56,0:17:20.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.37,0:17:32.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉和明日香学姐的演奏有些相似
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.85,0:17:34.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也这么觉得？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.52,0:17:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.42,0:17:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.69,0:17:46.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有客人在？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.99,0:17:51.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  能别放CD吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.64,0:17:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我不想听  讨厌它
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.42,0:18:05.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.15,0:18:09.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就别说你当初不想放弃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是讨厌吹奏乐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.97,0:18:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就别说那种话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.91,0:18:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今说什么当初不想放弃  太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.02,0:18:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.19,0:18:25.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸妈妈支付你的学费和房租供你上大学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.02,0:18:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你却说什么一直在忍耐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:35.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么可能懂我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.60,0:18:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.03,0:18:42.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.13,0:18:44.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.94,0:18:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是莫名其妙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.43,0:18:55.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心着凉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.80,0:18:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.57,0:19:13.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻美子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.47,0:19:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秀一？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.44,0:19:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长高了呢  真帅气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.66,0:19:23.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很受女孩欢迎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.03,0:19:25.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…没有啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.80,0:19:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问…久美子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.40,0:19:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她醒着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你按门铃应该就会帮你开门的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.88,0:19:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她朋友也在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.64,0:19:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.40,0:19:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻美子姐你有来听过我们演奏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.46,0:19:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这么问
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.63,0:19:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很希望你能来听一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.34,0:19:54.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关西大赛上的演奏好到让我们自己都惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就会去全国大赛演奏了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.52,0:19:59.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是要我去名古屋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.56,0:20:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是哦  确实有些勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.49,0:20:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:09.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想久美子应该很希望你能听一次她演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.84,0:20:14.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟她是因为憧憬你才开始吹奏乐的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.43,0:20:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,憧憬我？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:19.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不是一直挂在嘴边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.90,0:20:22.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好吹  总有一天和你一起演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.96,0:20:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.52,0:20:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  就一会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:28.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很吵的  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.30,0:20:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯吹给我听了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.56,0:20:39.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.57,0:20:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把这都忘记了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.07,0:21:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.97,0:21:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有CD吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.98,0:21:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么CD
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.83,0:21:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在吹的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.12,0:21:29.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二天  退了烧的我再次回到了练习当中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.26,0:21:29.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord2.5\fsp3}复活了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.28,0:21:31.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.88,0:21:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.31,0:21:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么今天的练习就到此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.21,0:21:39.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来有件事要告诉大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.31,0:21:43.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是本周末前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.45,0:21:46.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不能确定田中同学能继续参加社团活动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.32,0:21:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将会让中川同学代替她出场全国大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.13,0:22:04.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  下一首乐曲开始了
